{
  "3222020": {
    "name": "Crimson Quest",
    "steam_appid": 3222020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传统的 <strong>RTS（即时战略）</strong> 通常要求玩家管理多个基地和单位，跨多个战线进行多任务操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而 <strong>Crimson Quest</strong> 允许玩家控制一个<strong>自我维持的角色</strong>，这个角色可以<strong>生产多种怪物单位和战斗塔</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这使得一个小恶魔拥有了<strong>强大的生产能力</strong>，结合了<strong>即时探索 roguelike</strong>、轻度动作元素和丰富的策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个<strong>全新且独特的游戏类型</strong>，完美融合了传统 RTS 元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/bef39fc339e59001bb94e6c225e0f0e2.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/bef39fc339e59001bb94e6c225e0f0e2.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/bef39fc339e59001bb94e6c225e0f0e2.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过探索发现各种物品，并提前确定野外怪物的位置。<br>您可以打开地图标记目标区域，如果您已解锁侦查功能，还可以用它来监视远方区域！<br>如果想比敌方势力成长得更快，必须谨慎规划路线，避免浪费行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集资源创建怪物和塔。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以利用工人怪物开采散布在地图上的能源矿床，或打开附近的宝箱来获取资源！<br>随着怪物等级提升，<strong>它们需要更多矿石</strong>，而塔根据类型需要<strong>不同数量的资源</strong>。<br>您还可以将多余资源交给<strong>流动资源收集商</strong>换取其他资源，所以找到他的所在位置非常重要！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/36b081825881338e99c7fe409a6423f1.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=304 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/36b081825881338e99c7fe409a6423f1.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/36b081825881338e99c7fe409a6423f1.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/1937d64e931b5401c3029f6c22b0e3ba.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=304 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/1937d64e931b5401c3029f6c22b0e3ba.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/1937d64e931b5401c3029f6c22b0e3ba.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/516119a1be10e7daa8266cc6aa478e1c.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=304 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/516119a1be10e7daa8266cc6aa478e1c.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/516119a1be10e7daa8266cc6aa478e1c.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/72aab1306e13f06f95b06769542a7dd0.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=304 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/72aab1306e13f06f95b06769542a7dd0.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/72aab1306e13f06f95b06769542a7dd0.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>警惕敌方势力的成长。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择关卡时请谨慎。</strong><br>根据您选择的关卡，<strong>两个敌方阵营中的一个</strong>将会成长壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/0afb0d0f438d5cf8107757d0b9815d53.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=652 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/0afb0d0f438d5cf8107757d0b9815d53.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/0afb0d0f438d5cf8107757d0b9815d53.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/acdb390cfec42e1f6a5a90e3f9533372.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=652 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/acdb390cfec42e1f6a5a90e3f9533372.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/acdb390cfec42e1f6a5a90e3f9533372.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级您的盟友怪物。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过击杀敌方怪物或搜刮散布在地图上的怪物尸体来获取灵魂。<br>尽可能多收集灵魂，因为在关卡结算时，这些灵魂将被转换为相应怪物的<strong>征服经验值</strong>，帮助它们升级。<br>升级后的怪物可以学习<strong>召唤技能</strong>或在关卡开始时获得<strong>灵魂加成</strong>。<br>此外，达到最高等级的怪物将获得<strong>特殊增益效果</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/34cd0165eb4493839eeedd3d47671c02.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=638 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/34cd0165eb4493839eeedd3d47671c02.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/34cd0165eb4493839eeedd3d47671c02.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小心王国的英雄！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三名英雄会实时追踪您，逐渐缩短距离。<br>他们不会死亡，如果被击败会稍微撤退，但很快会继续追击。<br>与一般敌方势力不同，<strong>英雄会自行猎杀敌人以获取经验值</strong>。<br>每位英雄在经验值满后会获得<strong>独特技能</strong>。随着技能数量增加，他们会变得<strong>越来越强大且难以控制</strong>，因此尽早应对是最佳策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/3a47088dc2415513e8f4ddd08eff26b0.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/3a47088dc2415513e8f4ddd08eff26b0.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/3a47088dc2415513e8f4ddd08eff26b0.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>高效使用各种道具。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在宝箱和关卡奖励中获得的道具将对您的旅程提供极大的帮助。<br>道具可以大致分为<strong>消耗品和装备</strong>。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>消耗品</strong>包括各种药水，可<strong>恢复生命值</strong>、<strong>治疗异常状态</strong>并<strong>提供增益效果</strong>。您还可以使用<strong>陷阱对敌人造成伤害</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备</strong>则提供<strong>被动攻击方式</strong>，并通过其<strong>特殊能力</strong>为玩家带来战斗优势。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/6706e542ea9c427f5053d11d1f2e30b2.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/6706e542ea9c427f5053d11d1f2e30b2.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/6706e542ea9c427f5053d11d1f2e30b2.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>享受多样化的游戏风格。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开始您的冒险之前，您可以从多种模式中进行选择，以改变您的游戏风格。<br>通过这些模式，您可以成为战士、探险家，甚至是建筑师。<br>将您的角色转变为您选择的模式，开启新的方向并不断成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/7efa5f4447fdef20060e950d7133fcbd.poster.avif?t=1769538030\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/7efa5f4447fdef20060e950d7133fcbd.webm?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222020/extras/7efa5f4447fdef20060e950d7133fcbd.mp4?t=1769538030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
